The paper focuses on developing a computer-aided diagnosis approach using a convolutional neural network and attention mechanisms for histopathological images of the endometrium. This involves image analysis, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of machine learning algorithms and neural networks also suggests that the paper could belong to sub-categories such as information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), multimedia (cs.MM), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
